data.title: Experience the Spirit of Canada at Canada Place in Vancouver
data.meta_description: Immerse yourself in Canadian culture at Canada Place in Vancouver. Enjoy free activities like walking along the waterfront and exploring the Canadian Trail while taking in stunning views.
